379
01:09:02,399 --> 01:09:05,840
[SPEAKER_01] Žal mi je što sam 95.

380
01:09:06,159 --> 01:09:09,119
[SPEAKER_01] bio povrijeđen i nisam odigrao finale.

381
01:09:11,680 --> 01:09:14,960
